Package br.rio.puc.inf.builderSecurityObjective

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISecurityObjective
    Interface that defines the heading of the methods that compose a security objective
    ISecurityObjectiveProvider
    Class interface used to get the security objectives and add them to the framework
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseSecurityObjective
    Abstract class that implements the ISecurityObjective interface to create new security objectives in the framework
    ConfidentialitySecurityObjective
    Confidentiality security objective class that extends the BaseSecurityObjective class in order to define the attributes of the new objects
    DefaultSecurityObjectiveProvider
    Class that implements the ISecurityObjectiveProvider and defines the security objective and initialize it.
    IntegritySecurityObjective
    Integrity security objective class that extends the BaseSecurityObjective class in order to define the attributes of the new objects
    SecurityObjectivesExecution
    Class that allows to return the security objectives list of the framework
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SecurityObjectiveAcronym
    Enum type predefined to security objectives
